#: ../../developer/building/qubes-builder.rst:10
#: 667316f3d10a4359a17eb4ae42e8ce53
msgid ""
"**Note:** These instructions concern the older Qubes builder (v1). It "
"supports only building Qubes 4.2 or earlier.The build process has been "
"completely rewritten in `qubes-builder v2 <https://github.com/QubesOS"
"/qubes-builderv2/>`__      . This can be used for building Qubes R4.2 and"
" later, and all related components."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/building/qubes-builder.rst:12
#: b39cc061044d439cb55cc68cdc8a4a90
msgid ""
"**Note: See** :doc:`ISO building instructions </developer/building/qubes-"
"iso-building>` **for a streamlined overview on how to use the build "
"system.**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/building/qubes-builder.rst:14
#: d7eef8bb6d95437b8ef8597941bc8c3e
msgid ""
"We have a fully automated build system for Qubes, that downloads, builds "
"and packages all the Qubes components, and finally should spit out a "
"ready-to-use installation ISO, all in a `secure <https://www.qubes-"
"os.org/news/2016/05/30/build-security/>`__ way."
msgstr ""

